rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n越做越差，同埋好多間專揾生手笨柒。"},{"pid":"224dcf6507c4d493307a9866414b6bf24de965c3","tid":298431,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T11:26:57.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲打手打到來連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"499092006baf9da8758d5ab3ea24433aab37236a","tid":298431,"uid":35069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T11:34:32.000Z","msg":"近依邊果幾個大陸城市既海鮮街都貴架啦，已經無話抵食依樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}